detailedReviews.text: I was visiting the area and only got takeout several times and the grinder's were excellent. The last time I went there, an elderly woman was sitting behind the counter near the food pickup area. After I paid for my order and was leaving she quietly stopped me and whispered to me that I left too Big of a tip and it wasn't necessary. She's obviously had something to do with the ownership of the business. I quietly whispered back to her that I appreciate the service and that's just the way I am.
